# Health Check API Requests
# Use with the REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Basic Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Kubernetes-style Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### Ping Test
GET {{baseUrl}}/ping

### Readiness Probe
GET {{baseUrl}}/ready

### Liveness Probe
GET {{baseUrl}}/alive

### Comprehensive Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/health

### Individual Component Health Checks

# Database Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/health/database

# Memory Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/health/memory

# Redis Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/health/redis

# Filesystem Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/health/filesystem

# Dependencies Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/health/dependencies

# External APIs Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/health/external-apis

### Monitoring Endpoints (Require Authentication)

# Application Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Application Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Performance Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/performance
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Log Management (Require Authentication)

# Log Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/logs/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Manual Log Cleanup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/logs/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Manual Log Compression
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/monitoring/logs/compress
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Status Monitor Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/status